{{NRIS-only|date=November 2013}} {{Infobox NRHP | name = Ryan & Company Lumber Yard | image = Apopka Ryan Bros Lumber01.jpg | caption = | location = [[Apopka, Florida|Apopka]], [[Florida]] | coordinates = {{coord|28|40|18|N|81|30|27|W|display=inline,title}} | locmapin = Florida#USA | refnum = 93000074<ref name="nris">{{NRISref|version=2010a}}</ref> | area = | added = February 25, 1993 | visitation_num = | visitation_year = | governing_body = Private }} {{commons}}
The '''Ryan & Company Lumber Yard''' (also known as '''Ryan Bros., Inc.''') is a historic site in [[Apopka, Florida|Apopka]], [[Florida]]. It is located at 215 East Fifth Street. On February 25, 1993, it was added to the [[United States|U.S.]] [[National Register of Historic Places]].
